    <div id="titular"> 
     <p>Recerca i innovació</p> 
     <h2>PMF - Programa Martí Franquès d'ajuts a la investigació</h2> 
    </div> 
    <hr> 
    <!-- /titular --> 
    <div id="nav_sub"> 
    </div> 
    <hr> 
    <!-- /nav_sub --> 
    <div id="container_sub_sub"> 
     <div id="content_main"> 
      <p style="text-align:justify" class="MsoNormal"><strong><span class="hps">Atraure</span> <span class="hps"><span>el millor</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>talent</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>científic</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>al sud</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>de Catalunya</span></span></strong></p> 
      <p style="text-align:justify" class="MsoNormal"><span class="hps">La Universitat</span> <span class="hps"><span>Rovira</span></span><span class="hps"> i</span> <span class="hps"><span>Virgili</span></span><span>,</span> <span class="hps"><span>en col · laboració</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>amb</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>les</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>institucions</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>de recerca vinculades al</span></span> <span class="hpsatn"><span>Campus d'</span></span><span>Excel·lència Internacional</span> <span class="hps"><span>Catalunya Sud</span></span> <span class="hpsatn"><span>(</span></span><span>CEICS</span><span>)</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps"><span>posa en</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>marxa la segona edició del Programa</span></span> Martí i <span class="hps"><span>Franquès</span></span> d'ajuts a la investigació<span>,</span> <span class="hps"><span>una col·laboració</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>público-privada</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>dissenyada</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>per</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>atraure estudiants de</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>doctorat</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>i </span><span><span>investigadors </span>postdoctorals</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>de gran</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>talent</span><span> que</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>treballin</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>en projectes de recerca</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>interessants</span></span><span>.</span></p> 
      <p style="text-align:justify" class="MsoNormal"><span class="hps">Aquest programa</span> <span class="hps"><span>honora el</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>científic</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>Antoni</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>Martí i</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>Franquès</span></span> <span class="hpsatn"><span>(</span></span><span>Altafulla</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps"><span>1750</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>-</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>Tarragona</span></span><span>,</span> <span class="hps"><span>1832</span></span><span>)</span><span>,</span> <span class="hps"><span>que va fer</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>contribucions</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>notables</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>no només en els</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>camps</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>de la biologia</span></span><span>,</span> <span class="hps"><span>la física</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>i la química</span></span><span>,</span> <span class="hps"><span>sinó</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>també per al</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>desenvolupament</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>econòmic</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>del sud</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>de Catalunya</span></span><span>.</span> <span class="hps"><span>Va ser el</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>primer científic</span></span> en <span class="hps"><span>establir</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>amb</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>precisió la</span></span> <span class="hps"><span>composició de l'aire</span></span><span>.</span></p> 
      <ul> 
       <li><strong>Programa Martí i Franquès - Modalitat predoctoral</strong> 
        <ul>
         <br> 
         <li><strong>1a edició (maig 2014): tancada - 1st edition (may 2014): closed</strong></li> 
         <li><strong>2a edició (octubre 2014): tancada - 2nd edition (october 2014): closed</strong></li> 
         <br> 
        </ul> </li> 
       <br> 
      </ul> 
